# Logging
* Log every request that you receive that requires an action on your part.  Log requests in [cursor-log.md](mdc:cursor-log.md) in the root of the project.
* Follow the instructions in [cursor-log.md](mdc:cursor-log.md).  Remember to never delete or replace an existing entry.  Add new entries to the end, leaving two blank lines between entries.  Following the sample prompt provided.

